{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_015gxUm7z2UkmbBcprL2FevW","type":"tool_result","content":"# Issue Extraction: task-ui Implementation\n\n## Task IDs and Identifiers\n\n**Task ID:** `a780665e-b5c8-4df6-840f-71e121d99b74`\n\n**MCP Endpoint:** `http://localhost:9090/mcp/`\n\n**Repository:** `asdlc-repos/kaj-test-14182`\n\n**Issue Number:** #2\n\n## Key Information\n\nThis is an implementation task for a React-based task management UI component. The issue requests building a \"single-page task management interface\" with filtering, CRUD operations, and Nginx-based static serving on port 3000.\n\n**Core Requirements:**\n- Create a React 18 + TypeScript SPA using Vite\n- Implement task list display, add/edit/delete functionality\n- Support category and completion filtering\n- Highlight overdue tasks visually\n- Serve via Nginx with SPA fallback routing\n- Use `VITE_API_URL` environment variable for backend communication\n\n**Critical Constraints:**\n- No environment variables should be strictly required\n- The Dockerfile must use multi-stage builds\n- Button submission must be disabled during API requests\n- Overdue detection uses client-local date comparison (no timezone conversion)\n- Categories dropdown must refresh after mutations"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"2f27ef23-9ff9-47c5-8737-d226c025c699","uuid":"d88adc84-0358-4570-9628-7a7bc191b0cc","timestamp":"2026-04-23T09:55:34.931Z","tool_use_result":{"bytes":287333,"code":200,"codeText":"OK","result":"# Issue Extraction: task-ui Implementation\n\n## Task IDs and Identifiers\n\n**Task ID:** `a780665e-b5c8-4df6-840f-71e121d99b74`\n\n**MCP Endpoint:** `http://localhost:9090/mcp/`\n\n**Repository:** `asdlc-repos/kaj-test-14182`\n\n**Issue Number:** #2\n\n## Key Information\n\nThis is an implementation task for a React-based task management UI component. The issue requests building a \"single-page task management interface\" with filtering, CRUD operations, and Nginx-based static serving on port 3000.\n\n**Core Requirements:**\n- Create a React 18 + TypeScript SPA using Vite\n- Implement task list display, add/edit/delete functionality\n- Support category and completion filtering\n- Highlight overdue tasks visually\n- Serve via Nginx with SPA fallback routing\n- Use `VITE_API_URL` environment variable for backend communication\n\n**Critical Constraints:**\n- No environment variables should be strictly required\n- The Dockerfile must use multi-stage builds\n- Button submission must be disabled during API requests\n- Overdue detection uses client-local date comparison (no timezone conversion)\n- Categories dropdown must refresh after mutations","durationMs":4915,"url":"https://github.com/asdlc-repos/kaj-test-14182/issues/2"}}
