{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01QCeuu3QdWjDJrDMUZmSaxf","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The workspace is essentially empty (just a .logs directory). Let me set up the full React app from scratch.\n\nBased on the requirements:\n1. React 18 + TypeScript + Vite\n2. Axios for HTTP calls\n3. Tailwind CSS for styling\n4. VITE_API_URL environment variable (default: http://localhost:9090)\n5. Docker multi-stage build\n\nLet me plan the implementation:\n\n1. `package.json` - React 18, TypeScript, Vite, Axios, Tailwind\n2. `vite.config.ts` - Vite configuration\n\n\n3. TypeScript, Tailwind, and PostCSS configs to support the build pipeline\n4. Entry point files and the main App component\n5. API integration layer and type definitions\n6. UI components for displaying tasks, adding new ones, editing, and filtering\n7. Error handling with a dismissible banner\n8. Nginx configuration for serving the SPA on port 3000 with proper fallback routing\n9. Multi-stage Docker build for production deployment\n\nNow I'm thinking through the key implementation details: the API URL is injected at build time, overdue detection needs to use local dates to avoid timezone issues, the category filter should refetch data after mutations, the Add Task button should be disabled while requests are in flight, and I need confirmation dialogs for destructive actions like delete.\n\nLet me start building out all these files.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":208,"cache_read_input_tokens":24476,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":208,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"global"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"2f27ef23-9ff9-47c5-8737-d226c025c699","uuid":"65e08031-7190-406f-874b-c8342c3c79ec"}
