{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01A6984oCWjNWDjVVEiKwvDi","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01Dg3EqS34YbQeNL1pZrTzQz","name":"mcp__asdlc__submit_implementation","input":{"taskId":"a780665e-b5c8-4df6-840f-71e121d99b74","port":3000,"summary":"Implemented task-ui: a React 18 + TypeScript + Vite single-page application for task management served via Nginx on port 3000.\n\nKey features:\n- Task list with completion checkbox, category badge, due date label, and overdue highlighting (red text) using local date comparison (no UTC shift)\n- Filter bar with category dropdown (populated from GET /categories) and All/Incomplete/Complete status toggles\n- Add Task form with title (required), due date (optional), category (optional); submit button disabled during in-flight POST\n- Edit modal pre-filled with existing task data; Save calls PUT /tasks/{id}, Cancel dismisses\n- Delete with native browser confirmation dialog\n- Dismissible error banner for all API failures\n- Categories re-fetched after every create/edit mutation to stay in sync\n- VITE_API_URL baked in at build time via Vite's built-in VITE_* env var handling; Dockerfile ARG/ENV passes it through\n- Multi-stage Dockerfile: node:20-alpine builder → nginx:alpine with custom nginx.conf\n- Nginx config: listens on port 3000, try_files fallback to index.html for SPA routing, /health endpoint returning 200 OK","filesCreated":["package.json","tsconfig.json","tsconfig.node.json","vite.config.ts","tailwind.config.js","postcss.config.js","index.html","nginx.conf","Dockerfile",".dockerignore","src/main.tsx","src/App.tsx","src/types.ts","src/api.ts","src/index.css","src/components/AddTaskForm.tsx","src/components/EditModal.tsx","src/components/ErrorBanner.tsx","src/components/FilterBar.tsx","src/components/TaskCard.tsx"]},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creatio